  <brief_title>Intravenous (IV) Iron Preparation (VIT-45) in the Treatment of Restless Legs Syndrome (RLS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of a Novel Intravenous (IV) Iron Preparation (VIT-45) in the Treatment of Restless Legs Syndrome (RLS)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
