  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to evaluate the safety of 2 dosage regimens of Intravenous (IV)
      iron Ferric Carboxymaltose (FCM) in comparison to placebo in patients with Restless Legs
      Syndrome (RLS)
    </textblock>
